{"type": "article", "id": 51792, "title": "前 Dior 男装创意总监接管 Berluti，以及，Nike 发布马卡龙色 Air Force 1 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-04-04T04:22:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}, {"id": 44616, "name": "Ginza Six"}, {"id": 1352, "name": "Berluti"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180404120318siZL1VahCB8TmU5K.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/LVMH-taps-Kris-Van-Assche-for-Berluti,964103.html#.WsQ9mdNuYzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 任命前 Dior 男装创意总监接管 Berluti</strong></a> | 上周五，LVMH 集团旗下男装品牌 Berluti 的创意总监 Haider Ackermann 离职，有消息称前 Dior 男装创意总监 Kris Van Assche 将接任，目前这一消息得到了证实。在 2019 年 1 月的男装周上，Kris Van Assche 将发布他为 Berluti 设计的首个系列。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Victoria-Beckham-cuts-staff-numbers,963824.html#.WsRBVNNuYzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Victoria Beckham 裁员三分之一</strong></a> | 英国媒体称，Victoria Beckham 的个人品牌裁员 60 人，占总员工数的三分之一。这家公司去年亏损了 850 万英镑，品牌新的投资者 Neo Investment Partner 已经对它进行了战略管理分析。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/595000\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ginza Six 开业一周年，销售额破 600 亿日元</a></strong> | 即将在 4 月 20 日迎来一周年的日本百货商场 Ginza Six 发布数据显示，过去一年间总到访客流量达到 2000 万人，年销售额突破 600 亿日元。其中，海外游客呈增长趋势，今后预计会和香港、台湾等地区的高档购物中心合作，开展互相送客计划。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-north-face-launches-global-effort-to-celebrate-the-new-generation-of-female-explorers-300623105.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Move Mountains </a>是 The North Face 最新的产品营销活动，也是品牌首个以女性为重点的营销活动。该活动推出了一系列以女性运动员和其他知名女性为主角的短片，还与 Instagram 账号美国女童子军（GSUSA）合作创建了 12 个户外探险新成就徽章。 </p><p>除了营销活动外，The North Face 还透露了投资女性员工发展的计划，它承诺缩小赞助运动员队伍的性别薪资差距。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115757sp7FnLyt12oXGPCH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115757tUzyYPNm9A1dkh0n.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.699625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115835Za46kYThQ0S2vP8N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/uniqlo-karakami-karacho-ss18/#slide-16\" rel=\"nofollow\">优衣库早春系列</a>再发新品，这次从日本最古老的造纸工作室 karacho 获得灵感，用了传统的手工雕刻图案设计 T 恤和短裤。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115857dRZkiqt5r16Wz2By.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115859sbmTJ94nKFhtxAlp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115856uBkxywhVCDlI07zP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201804041158591QgBX6AOf0so3pyj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115857a9LocYiXhRgxrjIK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201804041158589rmf0zETbh7CJWRL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115858KaV51FnSElU973Bw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115858oilCnNuHQ6qbpV9v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115859nueDdl89673f2vUr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115858cAozUZlF8hCY1Dtg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115856IBUQxEqKJWaRO8X3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115856JmLGQ3xO1dVzcZK6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115857ncRh8ETDVw2k7FdO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115902ZnRELxfBi9cO0TJG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/stone-island-marina-ss18/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stone Island 发布 2018 春夏新品，</a>棉质圆领衫、尼龙运动外套、细条纹休闲裤和帽子，色彩还挺清新的。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115940HKqDOdLwcEplrboa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115940js3Hh0LrFA7PNfd9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115940Ow2AcXnWrBxaCTuj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115940CxZNldqLtKnhpAY2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115945oey7HgVI3NXmS1l6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115945Hp9wTRAzL17hQM8V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404115945CeYnv9uH8E0Mgic3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.400438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>复活节已经过了。Nike 才发布了复活节配色版<a href=\"https://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/nike-air-force-1-easter/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Air Force 1</a>，绒布鞋面拼接皮革，粉红色、蓝色和薄荷绿的马卡龙色搭配很抢眼。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120003Et7iuFA4O12a3nBS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666972\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120003aU8FTSpjkghfnwMe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667890\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上海时装周落幕。我们综合了潮流网站 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/shanghai-fashion-week-street-style/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Highsnobiety </a>和 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2018/4/street-style-2018-shanghai-fashion-week\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hypebeast </a>的街拍特辑，挑选了一些有意思的： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120028Pam86Z0vSkOMADgx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120028GqX2EZ8w0oOS1aP7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120033SIDopjuh6HJL7qUW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201804041200341Z4OQX8hRCij6r0g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120033e5dZTWO2G1S3Jp0q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018040412004503WqPTJRxz1pQXDe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180404120046WPp2ofKcXO0HYxij.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201804041200476NuZdqQYhFHrzaEW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Hypebeast</